{"tid":1764084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登泛民左膠之恥辱]廣東茂名示威者：香港人太軟弱，我們引以為鑒！","createTime":"2019-11-30T22:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T06:00:58.000Z","uid":241151,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"035416a9c602d84aacee8708fe44d756c473e2fa","tid":1764084,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T22:39:23.000Z","msg":"廣東茂名化州市文樓鎮居民近日與警方發生激烈衝突，當地政府以興建生態公園為名，欺騙老人簽字，後來改建火葬場和殯儀館，因而引發連場示威抗議。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在微博上傳影片，除紀錄當地示威場面外，更有示威人士的訪問片段。其中有示威者表示，政府欺騙人民，人民不能不反抗。提到示威者暴力程度甚高，受訪者就表示抗爭當然暴力，更有示威者認為香港示威者太軟弱，影響抗爭效果，令他們引以為鑒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論示威過程還是訪問片段，總之與是次事件相關的訊息，都不斷有人上傳微博及微信，但又極速被屏蔽。據指茂名現幾乎全民抗爭，不斷有人拿石頭擲向警察，警車大量被推翻，市面極其混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n七百萬港人最少有六百幾萬以為自己唔係港豬既港豬，有乜辦法唔死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfbb628101597936457f8b1c1499a22b4b3c2f7","tid":1764084,"uid":198590,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T22:39:35.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#241151 - 瀧野由美仔</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span>, 請大家多加注意, 善用不推文回覆！<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>人地學生就打生打死，鄺神都好自得其樂 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YW4Wctv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYW4Wctv.jpg&h=1310c14d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉&hellip;&hellip;唔好問我點解香港抗爭咁多年都係咁失敗，香港人情況仲越來越差<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fhaha.gif&h=20aa0304&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fno.gif&h=29da48de&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1714163/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1714163/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>想知乜嘢叫流水式...集會?流水就不可能集合，集合可能是在新屋嶺... - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>想知乜嘢叫流水式...集會?<br />\n流水就不可能集合，集合可能是在新屋嶺...<br />\n會唔會太過 creative, creative 到亂Q咁嚟。<br />\n定你哋較為喜愛嗌D無意思的口號，做無意義的事，好似時代革命，摺紙咁。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1696584/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1696584/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>改口號啦！[香港人！送頭！] - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>香港人！送頭！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1696549/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1696549/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>點呀？之前係咪話過要追究返邊d人，邊d網，邊d團體同傳媒吹市去送頭既？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2b0VZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2b0VZQ.jpg&h=2ac5df0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來係連登x蘋果吹雞<br />\n難怪有哂地點時間表<br />\n鑊鑊都港島，鑊鑊都推人去死<br />\n流人哋嘅血成就自己得票當選！<br />\n泛民蘋果全部都要仆街冚家鏟！<br />\n<br />\n好彩我一早就同班泛民左膠割晒蓆姐，分化實在好！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fsmile.gif&h=0b593ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快d回&quot;拉，不分化，不推文回覆啦&quot;<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>香港既和理非從來唔保護勇武，甚至會阻止勇武制服勇武出賣勇武，所以和理非實則係港奸 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>泛民港奸！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1661812/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1661812/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a>"},{"pid":"091e8ae763339efd3d22ccb491d3c18b96460cde","tid":1764084,"uid":98993,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T22:42:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca4eaa3bda043847e485e7b954bf157b5361eba2","tid":1764084,"uid":241151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T23:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36b9fe02d39c921bf4a642f9dde1598f74c112d","tid":1764084,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T23:40:54.000Z","msg":"佢哋做咗個榜樣畀我地睇<br />\n與其哂時間哂MP去燒/爆狗車，不如速戰速決推冧佢等佢無得用先"},{"pid":"9794fdd988cd72049d093eb0b3b5314912fc2b0d","tid":1764084,"uid":152394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T23:43:09.000Z","msg":"分夠未"},{"pid":"96378de730176968fa122d0222a24d883675f53b","tid":1764084,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2246eb72ab18c78bad52e1f92acafb5ce29ca122","tid":1764084,"uid":292119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"035416a9c602d84aacee8708fe44d756c473e2fa","tid":1764084,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T22:39:23.000Z","msg":"